  "subject": "VNFRQTS - Clarification for retries",
  "commit_message": "VNFRQTS - Clarification for retries\n\nThe reason for this is that there will be a number of internal retry Timers in a vendors implementation that will not make sense to expose externally, also where specifications have specified restricted retry behaviour.\n\nChange-Id: I5ba140b0008eb0595f094e25b48f9828eeb63165\nIssue-ID: VNFRQTS-183\nSigned-off-by: Bozawglanian, Hagop (hb755d) <hb755d@att.com>\n",
